<pre>
  STEPS
  - Open the dialog
  - click on the category field to open drop down
  - hit ESCAPE
  - the dropdown HTML should persist
  - the components are destroyed
</pre>

{{#paper-button onClick=(action 'open' 'case1')}}
  Open
{{/paper-button}}
Case 1 as form-select<br>

{{#if case1}}
  {{#paper-dialog class="flex-80" fullscreen="true" onClose=(action "close" 'case1') clickOutsideToClose=true}}
    {{#paper-select label="Category" required=true options=categories selected=category
        onChange=(action (mut category)) as |category|}}
      {{category}}
    {{/paper-select}}
  {{/paper-dialog}}
{{/if}}
